title: Videohive - After Effects Project Files - Mystic World
description:
Compatible with After Effects CS4 and above.
12 Image/video place holders.
16 text-holders.
Easy to use.
Easy to customize.
No plugins needed.
Full HD resolution 1080p, HD (720p) output comp is also included.
Duration: customizable, up to 3 minutes 22 seconds.
Separated in 14 scenes with adjustable duration, up to 15 seconds each.
Friendly interface.
Video tutorial included.
Color coded elements.
Texture overlay.
Elegant flares made directly in after effects with no additional plugins.
With some after effects knowledge, number of scenes can be easily increased.
